article_id:513,category_name:Events,title_name:Epilogue Added to the Echoes of Antiquity Raid Event,image_path:,message:<div>An epilogue has been added to the raid event Echoes of Antiquity, which ended <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1560319199"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>You can view the epilogue by tapping the banner on the upper-left corner of the Home screen, which can be accessed from the in-game footer menu, then selecting View Quests.</div><div><br></div><div>■Epilogue Availability</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1560319200"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1560923999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>■ Notes:</div><div>1. The epilogue can be viewed only by players who have completed up to chapter 5 of the event&rsquo;s story.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1560319200,update_time1559902225